{"id":928127,"xmlId":"JavaScript","name":"JavaScript and TypeScript","description":"<p>Provides support for working with JavaScript and TypeScript.\n    </p><h2>Features</h2>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Code completion</li>\n      <li>In-product documentation</li>\n      <li>Code formatting</li>\n      <li>Code inspections and quick fixes</li>\n      <li>Refactorings such as <i>Rename</i>, <i>Move</i>, <i>Extract Variable</i>, and more</li>\n      <li>Code snippets (<i>Live Templates</i>)</li>\n      <li>TypeScript Language Service support</li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <p>The plugin is bundled in IntelliJ IDEA, WebStorm, PhpStorm, PyCharm, RubyMine, GoLand, Rider, and CLion.\n    </p><h2>Getting started</h2>\n<p>Open your JavaScript or TypeScript project in the IDE or create a new one.\nThe JavaScript and TypeScript plugin will automatically detect the presence of related files and provide its features accordingly.\n</p><p>For more information on getting started, head over to the <a href=\"https://www.jetbrains.com/help/\">documentation</a> for your IDE.</p>\n<h2>Getting started</h2>\nOpen your JavaScript or TypeScript project in the IDE or create a new one. The JavaScript and TypeScript plugin will automatically detect the presence of related files and provide its features accordingly.\n<br>\nFor more information on getting started, head over to the <a>documentation</a> for your IDE.","organization":"JetBrains s.r.o.","tags":["Programming Language"],"version":"253.29346.240","dependencies":["com.intellij.modules.xml","intellij.css.common","intellij.xml.langInjection","intellij.css.common.psi","com.intellij.modules.spellchecker","intellij.css.backend","com.intellij.modules.scriptDebugger.ui","com.intellij.modules.ultimate","com.intellij.modules.css.backend","com.intellij.css","com.intellij.modules.json","com.intellij.modules.regexp"],"optionalDependencies":["org.intellij.plugins.markdown","com.intellij.modules.langInjection.backend","org.jetbrains.plugins.terminal","com.intellij.